code: @Override protected CamelContext createCamelContext() throws Exception {     CamelContext context = super.createCamelContext().     context.init().     // to force a different management name than the camel id     context.getManagementNameStrategy().setNamePattern("20-#name#").     return context. }

@Test public void testListComponents() throws Exception {     // JMX tests dont work well on AIX CI servers (hangs them)     context.init().     if (isPlatform("aix")) {         return.     }     MBeanServer mbeanServer = getMBeanServer().     ObjectName on = ObjectName.getInstance("org.apache.camel:context=20-camel-1,type=context,name=\"camel-1\"").     // list all components found in classpath     TabularData data = (TabularData) mbeanServer.invoke(on, "listComponents", null, null).     assertTrue("There should be more than 20 components", data.size() > 20). }

@Override protected RouteBuilder createRouteBuilder() throws Exception {     return new RouteBuilder() {          @Override         public void configure() throws Exception {             from("direct:start").to("log:foo").to("mock:result").         }     }. }
